DESCRIPTION:Interested in bringing Camp AIR to your team or organization?\n
	\n \n\nJoin this onboarding session to learn what it takes to plan\, launc
	h\, and facilitate a successful Camp AIR experience. We'll walk through th
	e program structure\, responsibilities\, available resources\, and support
	 options to help you run a successful Camp AIR in your team or organizatio
	n. \n\n \n\nDuring this session\, we will:\n\n*	Review the Camp AIR experi
	ence and outcomes\n*	Explain the roles of sponsors\, cohort and camp coach
	es\, and participants\n*	Discuss planning timelines and key milestones\n*	
	Share available tools\, templates\, and support resources\n*	Answer questi
	ons about running Camp AIR in your organization\n\nWhether you're ready to
	 launch a Camp AIR or simply exploring the possibility\, this session will
	 help you understand the process and next steps.\n\n \n\nWho should attend
	: Managers\, leaders\, learning champions\, and prospective Cohort Coaches
	 interested in bringing Camp AIR to their team or organization.\n\n \n\nOn
	ce you've decided to run a camp\, join our weekly Cohort Coach Office Hour
	s for ongoing guidance\, planning support\, and facilitation best practice
	s.\n\n \n\nWe look forward to helping you get started.\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n_
	__________________________________________________________________________
